Comparador - Class in mundo
This class takes the number generated by "elGenerador" sorts and compares it with the number given by the user, giving back to the interface the dots and comas array to be shown based on the wining way. the objective is to get the number which the program generated. once the player writes and compares the number, there will appear a dot for each number who is in the right place and a coma for each number in the wrong place, if the number is not in the objective number, there will not appear anything.
Comparador() - Constructor for class mundo.Comparador
This is the constructor, there, the relation is initialized, numeroDeCifras receives the first value of 4 and the value of generarNumero() in elGenerador is given to numeroObjetivo
